# Media Library Module

This module provides the portal-side foundation for:

- creating Media Library upload intents
- uploading file bytes directly to signed storage URLs
- completing uploads through the platform API
- listing, previewing, and archiving workspace media assets
- selecting existing assets through a reusable picker boundary

The module intentionally does not connect Assessment, Content Studio, or Learning Delivery yet.
